    "## 4. Reconstruct dates and clean the uploaded weather data\n",
    "\n",
    "The cleaned Beam files contain engineered calendar fields such as `pickup_day`, `pickup_month`, and `pickup_hour`.\n",
    "To merge with climate data, we reconstruct a full `pickup_date`.\n",
    "\n",
    "For weather, we use the uploaded **daily Meteostat CSV** covering January through May 2020, clean the columns, remove duplicates, retain Celsius values as required, and impute remaining missing weather values with daily medians."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
